{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.520", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.960", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist selbstverst\u00e4ndlich eine Freude f\u00fcr mich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der letzte Redner in diesem Jahr zu sein.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.320", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.080", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf Panama folgt nun das Paradies f\u00fcr Steuervermeider und gegebenenfalls -hinterzieher. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.200", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu diesem Schluss k\u00f6nnte man kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.920", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man die Berichte der Medien in den letzten Wochen und nat\u00fcrlich auch die eine oder andere Wortmeldung am heutigen Abend zur Kenntnis nimmt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.400", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.080", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch ich reibe mir die Augen in Anbetracht der Energie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.200", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die von internationalen Konzernen anscheinend nicht nur in die Entwicklung neuer Produkte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.400", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch in die Erarbeitung von Steuerumgehungsinstrumenten investiert wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.000", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieses erste Erstaunen weicht aber ziemlich schnell der Erkenntnis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.360", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.080", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es unser Bundestagspr\u00e4sident Dr.\u00a0Wolfgang Sch\u00e4uble in seiner Funktion als Finanzminister formulierte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.840", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "manchmal die Fantasie des Steuerzahlers gr\u00f6\u00dfer ist als die Regelungskraft des Gesetzgebers. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.360", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind also als Abgeordnete permanent dazu aufgerufen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.840", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Fantasie allzu findiger Personen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.920", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Konzerne und ihrer beratenden Kanzleien in die richtigen Bahnen zu lenken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.440", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Anbetracht von 194\u00a0Staaten auf dieser Erde und permanenter \u00c4nderungen in der Steuergesetzgebung ist das eine gro\u00dfe Herausforderung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.920", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der sich insbesondere wir Finanzpolitiker stellen m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.720", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Debatte sollten wir aber bei aller \u00f6ffentlichen Emp\u00f6rung genau abschichten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welchen weiteren Handlungsbedarf wir auf nationaler Ebene haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.760", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo wir auf europ\u00e4ischer Ebene mit unseren Partnern gemeinsam neue Regelungen schaffen m\u00fcssen und wo wir nur auf internationaler Ebene vorankommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.320", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.240", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in den sogenannten Paradise Papers wird eine Vielzahl von Sachverhalten angesprochen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.960", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir als nationaler Gesetzgeber zum Teil bereits in diesem Jahr aufgegriffen haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.920", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben Ma\u00dfnahmen ergriffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.080", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich auf die von der Presse angesprochenen F\u00e4lle noch gar nicht auswirken konnten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.840", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir t\u00e4ten also gut daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.240", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erst einmal die Wirkung dieser Ma\u00dfnahmen zu begutachten und dann vielleicht nach weiteren Schritten zu suchen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.280", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als Beispiel darf ich das Steuerumgehungsbek\u00e4mpfungsgesetz vom 23.\u00a0Juni dieses Jahres benennen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.720", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Steuerpflichtigen wie auch Kreditinstituten stark erweiterte Mitwirkungspflichten auferlegt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.200", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie Gesch\u00e4ftsbeziehungen zu Drittstaat-Gesellschaften unterhalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.320", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das aber auch deutlich erweiterte Ermittlungsbefugnisse der Finanzverwaltung beinhaltet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.280", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als zweites Beispiel sei genannt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.840", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir im Unterschied zu 16\u00a0anderen europ\u00e4ischen Mitgliedstaaten die Vierte EU-Geldw\u00e4scherichtlinie fristgerecht zum 26.\u00a0Juni 2017 umgesetzt haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.280", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dieser schaffen wir ein Transparenzregister, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.960", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem die wirtschaftlich Berechtigten von Unternehmen und Trusts entnommen werden k\u00f6nnen und das am 27.\u00a0Dezember dieses Jahres\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.720", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erst am 27.\u00a0Dezember\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.600", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an den Start geht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.960", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unmittelbar auf die Panama Papers hat die Bundesregierung einen Zehn-Punkte-Plan vorgelegt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.200", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der neben nationalen Ma\u00dfnahmen auch umfassende Initiativen auf internationaler Ebene vorsieht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.800", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutschlands Hartn\u00e4ckigkeit ist es dabei zu verdanken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.680", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich Panama jetzt an dem automatischen Informationsaustausch beteiligen wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.400", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die EU hat dieses Thema aufgegriffen und eine Liste mit nicht kooperativen Drittstaaten erstellt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.320", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um gemeinsam den Druck auf diese Staaten zu erh\u00f6hen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.320", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber auch EU-L\u00e4nder wie beispielsweise die Niederlande, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.240", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Malta oder Irland stehen in der Verantwortung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.360", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Abfluss von in Europa generierten Gewinnen zu unterbinden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.560", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gro\u00dfe Fortschritte haben wir auch beim automatischen Informationsaustausch gemacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.360", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der hier in Berlin am 29.\u00a0Oktober 2014 von 51\u00a0Staaten vereinbart und erstmals am 30.\u00a0September 2017, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.800", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also gerade vor wenigen Wochen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.080", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durchgef\u00fchrt wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.520", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mittlerweile sind 102\u00a0Staaten und Gebiete dem Abkommen beigetreten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.240", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen alles Erforderliche unternehmen und gemeinsam mit unseren Partnern Druck auf diejenigen Staaten aus\u00fcben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.000", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die immer noch der Auffassung sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schwarzgeld eine Heimat geben zu m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.560", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Abschlie\u00dfend sei gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.240", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir in der letzten Legislaturperiode vieles erreicht haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.600", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden uns weiterhin den Herausforderungen stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.760", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei hilft aber kein Aktionismus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.280", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern nur ein langer Atem."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.760", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich danke f\u00fcr Ihre Aufmerksamkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.320", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00fcnsche Ihnen ein frohes Weihnachtsfest, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.000", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und kommen Sie gesund ins neue Jahr."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.840", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke sch\u00f6n."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.760", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen herzlichen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.520", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lieber Kollege Feiler.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.400", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit schlie\u00dfe ich die Aussprache."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.880", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Interfraktionell wird \u00dcberweisung der Vorlagen auf den Drucksachen\u00a019/239, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.000", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "19/219, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.280", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "19/233 und 19/227 an den Hauptausschuss vorgeschlagen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.400", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind damit einverstanden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.680", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann sind die \u00dcberweisungen so beschlossen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.640", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind damit am Schluss der heutigen Tagesordnung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.240", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.840", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich w\u00fcnsche Ihnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.680", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch den Regierungsvertretern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.440", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "allen Mitarbeitern und Mitarbeiterinnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.960", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unseren Parlamentsassistenten und -assistentinnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.360", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Technikern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.520", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "all denen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.760", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die uns unsere Arbeit mit erm\u00f6glichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.520", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von ganzem Herzen besinnliche Weihnachten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.200", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gl\u00fcckliche Feiertage mit Ihren Liebsten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.200", 
   "children": [], 
